  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, W-SI-01)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is issued under the Minimal profile; a SHA-256 content hash is provided for reference but no digital signature is present, leaving structural integrity unverifiable (W-SI-01). All 13 credibility factors are assessed; seven show achieved levels below required levels and six are flagged as epistemic gaps at MRL 5. Decision outcome recorded as Accepted for synthetic test purposes.",
